---
title: Pork Sausage Spaghetti alla Positano with Tomato, Zucchini, and Lemon
description: Does your love for pasta know no bounds? We’ve got the perfect recipe for any self-professed carb connoisseur. Crispy pork sausage, tender bites of zucchini, jammy tomato, and a lemon-spiked garlic herb sauce are tossed with spaghetti for a dish that’s hearty, satisfying, and comforting. A sprinkle of Parmesan and chili flakes take the dish to new heights of bellissimo.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/2019-w20-r5-pork-sausage-and-garlic-herb-spaghetti-fbf6e1bf.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/2019-w20-r5-pork-sausage-and-garlic-herb-spaghetti-5ca4f4a2e3f33975f7019622-c4bee578.pdf
cuisine: North America
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/pork-sausage-spaghetti-alla-positano-5ca4f4a2e3f33975f7019622
servings: 2
author: Michelle Doll Olson
course: main course
time required: 30 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 990 kcal
  fat: 60 g
  saturated fat: 24 g
  carbohydrates: 82 g
  sugar: 10 g
